 What is @Autowired?
@Autowired is a Spring annotation used to automatically inject a bean (i.e., object) into another bean.

It's part of Dependency Injection â€” a core concept in Spring that helps manage how objects are connected.

ğŸ§  Think of it like this:
You say:

â€œHey Spring, I need this thing (a service, repo, etc.) â€” please wire it up for me!â€

And Spring replies:

â€œSure! I already have that bean created, Iâ€™ll inject it right here for you.â€

âœ… Example:
java
